Index the vault (scan and parse all files)

Usage: obsidian-cli-inspector index index [OPTIONS]

Options:
  -n, --dry-run          Perform a dry run without writing to database
  -f, --force            Force full re-index (ignores change detection)
  -o, --output <FORMAT>  Output in JSON format (for machine integration)
  -v, --verbose          Show verbose output
  -h, --help             Print help
